text: Serge Telle (born 5 May 1955) is a French diplomat. He was the Minister of State of Monaco from February 2016 until August 2020. Telle is a knight of the Legion of Honour and the National Order of Merit. He is also a commander of the Order of Saint-Charles. He was born in Nantes.
